<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٧٨٣ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(قط)</span> : <span class="c1">" فِي ذِكْرِ الْجَدِّ وَمِيرَاثِهِ "</span> الْحَدِيثَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">فِي تَرْجَمَةِ:</span> زَيْدِ بْنِ ثَابِتٍ، عَنْ عُمَرَ بْنِ الْخَطَّابِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>